casebody.data:
ARNAUDO BROTHERS
v.
AGRICULTURAL LABOR RELATIONS BOARD (United Farm Workers of America) S244322 Supreme Court of California MARCH 14, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled manner is transferred to the Fifth Appellate District with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of Tri-Fanucchi Farms v. Agricultural Labor Relations Board (2017) 3 Cal.5th 1161, 225 Cal.Rptr.3d 545, 405 P.3d 1110. ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
